snippet.title: Super Stream-Bara Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
You are a Capybara Streamer playing a platformer game where the main character, CAPPA, is a ropegun wielding Capybara trying to save their own kind from the Evil Zoo.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2651090/Super_StreamBara/

music by lesiakower - https://lesiakower.bandcamp.com/
